{"title":"2.8 AI 界面如何捕捉用户意图？","slug":"bip3979n0r58nrry","summary":"我们一起探索当用户输入内容时，能够捕捉用户意图的上下文提示模式。 上下文管理 是为 AI 模型提供背景信息，用于塑造 AI 行为和输出结果的最重要因素之一。当用户上传文档、提出问题或给出指令时，本质上是在教导 AI 模型怎么做事或者怎么提供哪种结果。尽管这一点非常重要，然而，大多","category":"2. AI-UX体验模式","tags":["PART4️⃣ AI驱动的体验设计方法&模式","2. AI-UX体验模式"],"featured":false,"order":64,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-09-25","wordCount":1769,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/bip3979n0r58nrry","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"ua618d11c\" id=\"ua618d11c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1935c9c2\" id=\"u1935c9c2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">我们一起探索当用户输入内容时，能够捕捉用户意图的上下文提示模式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3f347f8a\" id=\"u3f347f8a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805458097-74a2599a-e818-41b1-b81a-4e8ca9c1a494.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u20170740-d6f5-4894-b9e3-9d4108c2174%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A654%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f0f0f0%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf1aa4352%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u264f7d06\" id=\"u264f7d06\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7376b07\" id=\"uf7376b07\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">上下文管理</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u32f5cc50\" id=\"u32f5cc50\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">是为 AI 模型提供背景信息，用于塑造 AI 行为和输出结果的最重要因素之一。当用户上传文档、提出问题或给出指令时，本质上是在教导 AI 模型怎么做事或者怎么提供哪种结果。尽管这一点非常重要，然而，大多数的 AI 产品在处理上下文的方式却极为粗糙（绝大多数的 AI 产品，还需要用户掌握一定的提问和操作技能）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u670a5d13\" id=\"u670a5d13\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6abad48c\" id=\"u6abad48c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">目前，也有一些模式，如 Claude 主页的智能默认设置、GitHub Copilot 的上下文筛选，或 Adobe Firefly 的风格控制，都是很好的起点，但是，它们都存在局限性。智能默认设置要么过于宽泛，要么用户必须一开始就清晰表述完整意图，然后再通过反复的基于聊天的交互来完善上下文。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc31dc785\" id=\"uc31dc785\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf63327f7\" id=\"uf63327f7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">这样就造成了不必要的使用障碍。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5e606a6\" id=\"uc5e606a6\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua9d7cf11\" id=\"ua9d7cf11\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">想一想，常见的使用场景：一位金融分析师上传了一份季度报告后，仍然，需要详细说明要提取哪些内容。又或者在 Perplexity 上搜索跑鞋的购物者，得到的结果依然宽泛、缺乏针对性，必须根据自己的偏好手动筛选。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7f0454b0\" id=\"u7f0454b0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u44779f96\" id=\"u44779f96\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">既然上下文对于 AI 生成的结果影响如此重要，那么，为什么我们还让用户如此费力地去提供呢？</span><span data-lake-id=\"uad8704ae\" id=\"uad8704ae\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">🤔</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u559df4c2\" id=\"u559df4c2\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf6bd14be\" id=\"uf6bd14be\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">与之相反，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3714d78a\" id=\"u3714d78a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">预测性用户体验（Predictive UX）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0646e9ce\" id=\"u0646e9ce\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提供了另一种思路。系统无需等待用户阐述每一个步骤，而是可以在用户输入时，依据其行为或常见模式预测意图。比如，苹果提醒（Apple Reminders）会在你输入时推荐可能的任务；Grammarly 会预测错误并直接给出修正建议；Gmail 的智能撰写（Smart Compose）甚至能预测完整短语，极大减少了撰写邮件的障碍。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u42a13309\" id=\"u42a13309\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805458070-1c5493be-4fe6-4d73-a8a5-b45885c4157a.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc3e4fa35-98a2-4e45-ae2a-95246df0ff3%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A627%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f5f5f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6f615b16%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6a6aaf04\" id=\"u6a6aaf04\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud4308052\" id=\"ud4308052\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">接下来，我们一起探讨 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8a91181a\" id=\"u8a91181a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">内联意图优化</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u22418278\" id=\"u22418278\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，展示 AI 系统如何在搜索、信息提取和内容创作等核心用例中，在用户输入时预测并呈现最有用的提示优化内容。其目标是缩短实现价值的时间，并且将 AI 重塑为一个能够在用户输入时预测其意图的自适应伙伴。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucfc4617d\" id=\"ucfc4617d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6c1aedad\" id=\"u6c1aedad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"O1PWB\" id=\"O1PWB\"><span data-lake-id=\"u33caf064\" id=\"u33caf064\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1. 搜索工作流上下文</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u5883239d\" id=\"u5883239d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua27bbc41\" id=\"ua27bbc41\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">随着 Perplexity 和 ChatGPT 这类平台基于 AI 的搜索功能不断迭代增强，我们可以把大多数查询归入几个可预测的类别。如果系统能够预测意图，就应该以标签、滑块或下拉菜单的形式呈现上下文提示，用于引导用户优化搜索，并减少产品使用障碍。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucf86c66d\" id=\"ucf86c66d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4aea3543\" id=\"u4aea3543\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">针对常见用例的一些设计方法如下：</span></p><ul list=\"ubf4e733b\"><li fid=\"u79ab37f8\" data-lake-id=\"u45dc6dae\" id=\"u45dc6dae\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u66740df3\" id=\"u66740df3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">搜索跑鞋时，通过 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud2fc61bb\" id=\"ud2fc61bb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">上下文预设 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf19dcaf2\" id=\"uf19dcaf2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7c5f2221\" id=\"u7c5f2221\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">下拉菜单选择 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u56283ecb\" id=\"u56283ecb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">地形类型（公路、小径、跑步机）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u86cc7f7d\" id=\"u86cc7f7d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805458115-dd932f79-059f-47dd-8d77-8c40ad0cbadb.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5b4fc35b-a69a-4e3f-bad8-90c08ddbaef%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A440%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f7f7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u185f1ceb%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u3389d89e\"><li fid=\"u454f9d9c\" data-lake-id=\"uc8d3e840\" id=\"uc8d3e840\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3d773b88\" id=\"u3d773b88\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)\">在本地搜索餐厅时，利用 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udcae9a36\" id=\"udcae9a36\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)\">二维距离选择器 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u14535319\" id=\"u14535319\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)\">和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9adfaefd\" id=\"u9adfaefd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)\">切换下拉菜单</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud6df0834\" id=\"ud6df0834\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)\">，按距离和氛围筛选餐厅。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u61c7024a\" id=\"u61c7024a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805458101-285bfeaa-b14a-4bee-971e-7a4be6d7fc8f.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u69294b04-df0f-4b44-a346-f7d6dd3212e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A450%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f7f7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4dc08313%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u41838644\"><li fid=\"u9fc7873f\" data-lake-id=\"uc05fad73\" id=\"uc05fad73\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"udab18db9\" id=\"udab18db9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">追踪特斯拉股票时，使用 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc49a6ad7\" id=\"uc49a6ad7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">下拉菜单 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8afe19b1\" id=\"u8afe19b1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u08cb5b55\" id=\"u08cb5b55\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">分段范围选择器</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubdc19049\" id=\"ubdc19049\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，在不同信息源（雅虎、彭博社、美国全国广播公司财经频道）或时间区间之间切换。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uf9408456\" id=\"uf9408456\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805458055-6bb11a09-84f1-4696-830b-0d1ea7d88791.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u43a96386-6951-42cd-b082-41127af3849%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A450%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f7f7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf17692f4%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u6a825964\"><li fid=\"u03ea4dcb\" data-lake-id=\"u822d192c\" id=\"u822d192c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4a95b9e3\" id=\"u4a95b9e3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">询问 “什么是 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u799aab98\" id=\"u799aab98\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AI 用户体验</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4db9edd0\" id=\"u4db9edd0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">？” 时，通过 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucd4f8a97\" id=\"ucd4f8a97\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">上下文默认设置 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5474793f\" id=\"u5474793f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u20031265\" id=\"u20031265\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">嵌套下拉菜单</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u75fdfae0\" id=\"u75fdfae0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，调整回答长度、面向受众（设计师、工程师、创始人）或回答深度。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u21e6ccee\" id=\"u21e6ccee\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805458687-f941526d-8d8a-48d3-825d-c700d03a9919.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u1285e5f3-1c02-4fec-a232-2be4cecf99f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A450%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f7f7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u5f0a0062%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9e667c74\" id=\"u9e667c74\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"udba7a057\" id=\"udba7a057\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">...</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub33bd44a\" id=\"ub33bd44a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0778d8f9\" id=\"u0778d8f9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"Aofww\" id=\"Aofww\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4a8fdf07\" id=\"u4a8fdf07\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2. 文件上传上下文</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u47b4f2ef\" id=\"u47b4f2ef\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue6f3bd6f\" id=\"ue6f3bd6f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">当用户上传文件时，系统不会闲置，而是会立即显示根据该</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6f73f510\" id=\"u6f73f510\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">文件类型定制的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue6de70f6\" id=\"ue6de70f6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">、</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued9b0810\" id=\"ued9b0810\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">感知上下文的提示</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4d4b7617\" id=\"u4d4b7617\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u41b69c77\" id=\"u41b69c77\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5eeaa06d\" id=\"u5eeaa06d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">展示这些智能默认设置的两种方法如下：</span></p><ul list=\"uf0b9202b\"><li fid=\"uc80896bc\" data-lake-id=\"ud4e121fb\" id=\"ud4e121fb\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc8dbc3cd\" id=\"uc8dbc3cd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">嵌套提示预设</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u96f6b76c\" id=\"u96f6b76c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，呈现可展开的菜单，将相关选项聚类（例如，“总结” 可展开为 “关键要点”“要点列表”“章节总结”），帮助用户梳理结构化的多步骤工作流程。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u137af4be\" id=\"u137af4be\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805458695-05effe46-098c-4a0a-af45-2252b300dacd.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uac2f7472-8bac-4b90-bbf1-c8406269580%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A449%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8f8f8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud1567d9c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u9468e2aa\"><li fid=\"u8f131ee8\" data-lake-id=\"ud6994b74\" id=\"ud6994b74\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u18ac3834\" id=\"u18ac3834\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">内联占位文本</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u66d329fe\" id=\"u66d329fe\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，显示轻量级且贴合文件上下文的提示（例如，针对图片显示 “让我描述、提取文本或重新组合”，针对视频显示 “让我总结场景、添加字幕”），让用户自然且直观地知道下一步该做什么。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uc7823c42\" id=\"uc7823c42\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805459049-009727e0-8fdd-4c19-91ec-08210167ea09.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7ca5db0c-44bf-4399-955c-f51e1ce2f85%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A449%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud5b674ea%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u66e841a0\" id=\"u66e841a0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u16dd6670\" id=\"u16dd6670\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">这种设计将文件上传从一个被动行为转变为一个交互式入口，让 AI 引导用户获得有价值的结果。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3fba98b1\" id=\"u3fba98b1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc283f476\" id=\"uc283f476\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">...</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub769bc11\" id=\"ub769bc11\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubbcfed94\" id=\"ubbcfed94\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"jv8Z4\" id=\"jv8Z4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf29d5189\" id=\"uf29d5189\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">3. 内容创作上下文</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u96efbd6c\" id=\"u96efbd6c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u12f9abdf\" id=\"u12f9abdf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">当用户进行内容创作时，AI 可以展示上下文提示，用于调整语气、风格和格式，减少 “空白页面” 带来的阻碍，引导用户生成符合需求的内容。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u051aa06b\" id=\"u051aa06b\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ued9fd194\" id=\"ued9fd194\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">以下是一些独特的方法：</span></p><ul list=\"u0905cfa1\"><li fid=\"u5f10f55b\" data-lake-id=\"ue4de3991\" id=\"ue4de3991\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0e4edf2b\" id=\"u0e4edf2b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">使用 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u08935e8d\" id=\"u08935e8d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">二维语气调节器，</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d0794a0\" id=\"u2d0794a0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">通过快捷滑块或选择器来调整邮件语气（如从随意 - 有说服力，或从正式 - 专业）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u8ae8815c\" id=\"u8ae8815c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805459051-69882761-b3a8-4c1d-a323-1bdeb43489be.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ufc1ce3e1-a98f-4db6-9956-30a8f733d21%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A448%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8f8f8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub437f92a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u50d552fa\"><li fid=\"ua847e88c\" data-lake-id=\"u82e5c7e5\" id=\"u82e5c7e5\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c6bf4bf\" id=\"u3c6bf4bf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">利用 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d532c43\" id=\"u2d532c43\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">滑块控件 </span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u427226fb\" id=\"u427226fb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">选取图像属性，如宽高比或变体（如故事用 9:16，帖子用 1:1）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ubc8addbf\" id=\"ubc8addbf\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805459064-d0f5a30f-9e82-4c8c-8361-fa6a87139635.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0b1a734c-0694-4476-9c14-7ec0b012ced%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A450%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u7d0f9e5d%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"ucccad26f\"><li fid=\"uaabd5737\" data-lake-id=\"u5efdefa7\" id=\"u5efdefa7\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"udc9a58c2\" id=\"udc9a58c2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在视频生成时，通过</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udadf952d\" id=\"udadf952d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">下拉菜单选择堆叠式提示</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf6a4a494\" id=\"uf6a4a494\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，以选取相机角度（如中景、特写、鸟瞰）来控制画面构图。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ufbb61c82\" id=\"ufbb61c82\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805459445-5782c279-532e-4d34-be48-09a282211c6a.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u935a9f91-bf2e-49f9-ac52-d4b455ed18e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A448%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u248e2226%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><ul list=\"u6457a396\"><li fid=\"ub64b81a7\" data-lake-id=\"u34573a3c\" id=\"u34573a3c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub4ab6321\" id=\"ub4ab6321\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在起草领英帖子时，通过</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0aded91a\" id=\"u0aded91a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">内联提示建议</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5484a71c\" id=\"u5484a71c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">添加主题标签（如 AI 用户体验、产品设计），从而引导内容方向。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uc67ba2b1\" id=\"uc67ba2b1\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1758805459517-6e377c0d-5a89-4762-9ff9-6cc45baad019.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u61828d5d-8761-414f-ad07-2d0ca896377%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u59228536-44b5-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A451%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8f8f8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u761f3804%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"udd35e36c\" id=\"udd35e36c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff4edf2a\" id=\"uff4edf2a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">这些实践表明了一个根本性转变：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud84c24ee\" id=\"ud84c24ee\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">当 AI 界面能够预判，而不是仅仅做出反应时，才真正变得智能</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6968e17e\" id=\"u6968e17e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">。不需要等待用户给出完美指令，上下文用户界面模式可自然呈现用户意图，无论是针对文件上传的自适应预设、搜索的动态优化标签，还是内容创作的内联语气控制。这样一来，用户花在解释需求上的时间减少，而能将更多时间用于优化重要结果。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u743f93af\" id=\"u743f93af\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8b918dbb\" id=\"u8b918dbb\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb3b7bf3\" id=\"ucb3b7bf3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">设计 AI 界面要能领会言外之意，而不只是关注表面文字。如果做到这一点，不仅能提升用户体验，还能从根本上重新定义人类与 AI 系统的沟通方式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0fe61a2d\" id=\"u0fe61a2d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc2fbd5d\" id=\"ufc2fbd5d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span><br></p><blockquote data-lake-id=\"u1cc48bbd\" id=\"u1cc48bbd\"><p data-lake-id=\"ua52e6dca\" id=\"ua52e6dca\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub6383ef2\" id=\"ub6383ef2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">原文链接：<br /></span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SMkSF6vsDwmQ3khIjX1uRQ\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"udbbe8e54\" id=\"udbbe8e54\"><span data-lake-id=\"uac0346b4\" id=\"uac0346b4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SMkSF6vsDwmQ3khIjX1uRQ</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u3112fec6\" id=\"u3112fec6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"><br /></span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/how-can-ai-ui-capture-intent-d7a6d0393ded\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u50795af5\" id=\"u50795af5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua5b60325\" id=\"ua5b60325\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://uxdesign.cc/how-can-ai-ui-capture-intent-d7a6d0393ded</span></a></p></blockquote>"}
